{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I want you to talk to them and make them wait, because I'm running home for a gun.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, I knew that he was going to kill them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So when I saw them coming, I could not stop to tell them, don't go, he's going to kill you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because that means, why would I save Jews?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I must be Jewish myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A stranger in the village, and-- and warning the Jews not to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in passing by, I said, run back to the forest because they came out of the forest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, run back to the forest, and I kept going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this man came on the bicycle-- the one with the gun-- came on the bicycle, and they-- they didn't hear me right.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they starting asking, what, what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I couldn't stop with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could not stop to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, not knowing me, what they did to me, they said to the man, we will not go with you because you're going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't tell them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew what they were going to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no time to tell them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I just told them, run back to the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from that day on, it started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, towards the end of the war, he kept quiet, he went to the underground, to the AK, which is [NON-ENGLISH] in Poland, and he told them that he's suspicious of me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would come and interview me and ask me, and couldn't prove anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But finally he decided that if I-- if he doesn't do something for-- with me, if I am Jewish, then if the Russians come in, I'll tell them, and they'll kill him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went to Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
